		<th class="PanelHeader" align="Left" height="25" width="100">&nbsp;Author</th><th class="PanelHeader" align="Left" width="85%">&nbsp;Thread: Wierd idea I have regarding mob camping...</th>
	</tr><tr>
		<td class="PanelBody" nowrap="nowrap" valign="Top" width="150"><table border="0">
			<tr>
				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="shpiffey is not online. Last active: 5/21/2005 1:26:32 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=shpiffey">shpiffey</a><br></td>
