				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Wierd idea I have regarding mob camping...<a name="58807"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 24 04 12:45 PM</span></td>
